name: Couple NFTs - Pair #2 - I LOVE YOU
description: This Couple NFT(s) is an mp4 file of an animated cartoon couple whose world becomes filled with color because of their love for each other. Couple NFTS are my creations that have only 2 editions. Thus, only two of this design will exist in the whole world. These are meant for couples. Like the way couples wear couple shirts, I hope my couple NFTs will also be a way of showing love to your beloved. You can just buy one for yourself and try to find the one who has the same design, hoping you would be a couple. Or, if you already have someone special, you can buy the pair and give one to your beloved.
